                      "textoBloco":"<p dir=\"ltr\">A praia fluminense de Ita&uacute;na, em Saquarema, e a catarinense Praia da Ferrugem, Garopaba, foram palcos da primeira e da segunda etapa, respectivamente do Circuito Banco do Brasil de Surfe 2023.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Na Praia de Ita&uacute;na, onde aconteceu a abertura, em 24 de abril, tivemos quatro vit&oacute;rias do Brasil, com destaque para Tain&aacute; Hinckel e Ian Gouveia, que receberam o Trof&eacute;u Leo Neves, produzido especialmente para eternizar os campe&otilde;es do <a title=\"\" href=\"https://worldsurfleague.us9.list-manage.com/track/click?u=9c75f4cf1e19118d57c2f963e&amp;id=b13a4cd881&amp;e=5020ec3dc4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Saquarema&nbsp;Surf&nbsp;Festival</a> e largaram na frente no Circuito Banco do Brasil.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img $img0$ /></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"content-inline-image content-inline-image--large content-inline-image--left\"><span class=\"content-image-caption content-image-caption-below content-image-caption--align-left\"><em>Tain&aacute; Hinckel e a peruana campe&atilde; do Pro Junior, Kalea Gervasi</em> <span class=\"photographer\"> - WSL / Heusi Action</span></span></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img $img1$ width=\"607\" height=\"341\" /></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"content-inline-image content-inline-image--large content-inline-image--left\"><span class=\"content-image-caption content-image-caption-below content-image-caption--align-left\"><em>Finalistas do QS 5000: Luel Felipe, Ian Gouveia, Tain&aacute; Hinckel e Sophia Medina </em> <span class=\"photographer\"> - WSL / Heusi Action</span></span></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><br /><span class=\"content-inline-image content-inline-image--large content-inline-image--left\"><span class=\"content-image-caption content-image-caption-below content-image-caption--align-left\"><span class=\"photographer\">Confira mais informa&ccedil;&otilde;es sobre a etapa de Saquarema </span></span></span><a title=\"\" href=\"https://www.worldsurfleague.com/events/2023/lt/143/circuito-banco-do-brasil-saquarema-surf-festival/main\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">aqui</a>.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">J&aacute; no doming&atilde;o de sol do dia 7, na Praia da Ferrugem, Garopaba, em Santa Catarina, local da segunda fase do Circuito, Laura Raupp e o campe&atilde;o mundial Adriano de Souza s&atilde;o os novos vencedores da etapa.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" $img2$ width=\"623\" height=\"415\" /></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Adriano de Souza e Laura Raupp com os trof&eacute;us das vit&oacute;rias em Garopaba (Cr&eacute;dito da Foto: @WSL / Daniel Smorigo)</em></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><br /><span class=\"content-inline-image content-inline-image--large content-inline-image--left\"><span class=\"content-image-caption content-image-caption-below content-image-caption--align-left\"><span class=\"photographer\">Confira mais informa&ccedil;&otilde;es sobre a etapa de Garopaba </span></span></span><a title=\"\" href=\"https://www.worldsurfleague.com/events/2023/qs/154/circuito-banco-do-brasil-de-surfe-garopaba/main\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">aqui</a>.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Remando juntos para o Futuro &eacute; o lema do Circuito Banco do Brasil de Surfe </strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As pr&oacute;ximas etapas est&atilde;o marcadas para o m&ecirc;s de agosto e os locais ainda ser&atilde;o anunciados. V&aacute;rias atividades recreativas est&atilde;o programadas para receber o p&uacute;blico das praias. Aulas de surfe com monitores em diferentes n&iacute;veis, espa&ccedil;o kids para entreter as crian&ccedil;as, beach t&ecirc;nis, futev&ocirc;lei, fitdance, al&eacute;m de pr&aacute;tica de yoga e exerc&iacute;cio funcional, ativa&ccedil;&otilde;es de educa&ccedil;&atilde;o e preserva&ccedil;&atilde;o ambiental. Quem esteve em Saquarema ainda pode acompanhar uma exposi&ccedil;&atilde;o do CCBB. Confira o que rolou nos dias do evento:</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"tiny-carrossel-container wide\" contenteditable=\"false\">\n<div class=\"slideshow-container\">\n<div class=\"mySlides\" style=\"display: block;\">\n<div class=\"numbertext\">1 / 7</div>\n<div class=\"image-slide wide\" style=\"background-image: url('https://s3.servicos.bb.com.br/pns1ibbdf001/midia/d769a758f087752f146f3bd88284cc6da903ff98f9bade26213d99f0da0d03e1-CROP.jpeg?refresh=1683716318648');\" title=\"\" role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"text\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mySlides\" style=\"display: none;\">\n<div class=\"numbertext\">2 / 7</div>\n<div class=\"image-slide wide\" style=\"background-image: url('https://s3.servicos.bb.com.br/pns1ibbdf001/midia/c95739ed80aa12363bc9d75d29208f758fa5fdf4c627fc0636235a36fec1f6d4-CROP.jpeg?refresh=1683716353656');\" title=\"\" role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"text\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mySlides\" style=\"display: none;\">\n<div class=\"numbertext\">3 / 7</div>\n<div class=\"image-slide wide\" style=\"background-image: url('https://s3.servicos.bb.com.br/pns1ibbdf001/midia/d5c91ec89eb18ed165f2aaa24b0d523db95cfe9516853dcc6698d2b32b5587f1-CROP.jpeg?refresh=1683716369114');\" title=\"\" role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"text\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mySlides\" style=\"display: none;\">\n<div class=\"numbertext\">4 / 7</div>\n<div class=\"image-slide wide\" style=\"background-image: url('https://s3.servicos.bb.com.br/pns1ibbdf001/midia/94f93311f6a3f0620fe23cdd27812c2bf17b4cbc9be17db8ea6df1d585a7d65b-CROP.jpeg?refresh=1683716381543');\" title=\"\" role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"text\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mySlides\" style=\"display: none;\">\n<div class=\"numbertext\">5 / 7</div>\n<div class=\"image-slide wide\" style=\"background-image: url('https://s3.servicos.bb.com.br/pns1ibbdf001/midia/1c3ac854cedb8d789617031f59625ad046ad378e43deb6ad7d75aad74be17b17-CROP.jpeg?refresh=1683716393333');\" title=\"\" role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"text\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mySlides\" style=\"display: none;\">\n<div class=\"numbertext\">6 / 7</div>\n<div class=\"image-slide wide\" style=\"background-image: url('https://s3.servicos.bb.com.br/pns1ibbdf001/midia/d744f83972b57df31fd03a34b9fc609084b5901dadc502edfd7e97697e11328f-CROP.jpeg?refresh=1683716403598');\" title=\"\" role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"text\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mySlides\" style=\"display: none;\">\n<div class=\"numbertext\">7 / 7</div>\n<div class=\"image-slide wide\" style=\"background-image: url('https://s3.servicos.bb.com.br/pns1ibbdf001/midia/a252488e7f70d6a315b9f0939549cc0cef5711241fa31fd0678263348433b157-CROP.jpeg?refresh=1683716414877');\" title=\"\" role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"text\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<a class=\"navigator-btn prev\">â®</a> <a class=\"navigator-btn next\">â¯</a></div>\n<div class=\"dot-box wide\">\n<div class=\"dot active\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"dot \">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"dot \">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"dot \">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"dot \">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"dot \">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"dot \">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"end\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>",
